Package: climateAnalyzeR
Title: Import Data from ClimateAnalyzer.org into R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Van Scoyoc",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matthew_vanscoyoc@nps.org",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6821-4476"))
Description: This package imports data from ClimateAnalyzer.org into R. It is 
    currently under development and only imports temperature and precipitation 
    data and soil water balance data.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0),
    readr (>= 1.4),
    tidyr (>= 1.1.2),
    XML (>= 3.99)
